Paper: hep-th/9710012

Date: 1997-10-02

Title: Nontopological structures in the baby-Skyrme model

Authors: B. Piette and W.J. Zakrzewski

Comments: latex, 4 pages. Proceedings of the Soliton conference (Kingston 1997)

We report our observations that the baby-Skyrme model in (2+1) dimensionspossesses non-topological stationary solutions which we call pseudo-breathers.We discuss their properties and present our results on their interaction withthe topological skyrmions.